measure.CatchLine: Limits the circumstances under which a landlord may disclose confidential information.
measure.MeasureSummary:
Digest: This Act limits the private information that a landlord can share. (Flesch Readability Score: 64.9). 
	Limits the circumstances under which a landlord may disclose confidential information. Authorizes statutory damages for individuals affected by knowing violations. 
	Takes effect on the 91st day following adjournment sine die.
measure.RelatingToFull: Relating to landlord disclosure of confidential information; and prescribing an effective date.
measure.RelatingTo: Relating to landlord disclosure of confidential information; prescribing an effective date.
